gameboy-eval — third-party assets and attribution
==================================================

This benchmark vendors and/or fetches third-party assets that are published for
the purpose of testing Game Boy emulators. Each is used under its own license;
originals and licenses are retained in their respective fetched directories.

Reference emulator / oracle
---------------------------
- SameBoy — https://github.com/LIJI32/SameBoy — MIT License.
  Used as a BLACK-BOX oracle (never as a source reference for candidates).
  SameBoy ships its own open-source Game Boy boot ROM, which we use for BOTH
  the oracle and candidates. The original Nintendo boot ROM is NEVER shipped.

CPU test vectors (optional internal CPU smoke-test only)
--------------------------------------------------------
- SingleStepTests/sm83 — https://github.com/SingleStepTests/sm83
- adtennant/GameboyCPUTests — https://github.com/adtennant/GameboyCPUTests

Procedural test ROMs
--------------------
- c-sp/game-boy-test-roms — https://github.com/c-sp/game-boy-test-roms
  (aggregates Blargg, Mooneye, dmg-acid2/cgb-acid2, Mealybug Tearoom, etc.)
- Gekkio/mooneye-test-suite — https://github.com/Gekkio/mooneye-test-suite — MIT.
- mattcurrie/dmg-acid2, mattcurrie/cgb-acid2.
- Suite metadata: adtennant/GameboyTestSuites.

